oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Loy McCormick's Gospel Concert with the Foggy River Boys at the Inverness High School Stadium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Gospel music; McCormick Brothers; Foggy River Boys (Musical group);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (blue on white) announcing Loy McCormick's Gospel Concert with the Foggy River Boys and the Camp Meeting Boys at the High School Stadium on July 10. Poster features metal photoplates of the Foggy River Boys and the camp Meetings Boys and Loy McCormick.
